Package: sweets
Title: Disposition Tables and Listings for Clinical Pharmacokinetic Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Steve", "Hummel", , "steve.hummel@simulations-plus.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a toolkit for building clinical pharmacokinetic (PK) data
    disposition tables and deletion listings. Counts and reports records excluded
    during the data build process using DELFN deletion flag variables, producing
    audit-ready disposition tables and pooled summaries. Also includes utilities
    for reading and archiving data files, summarizing dataset contents, and
    generating formatted deletion listing reports.
